This model wrapper integrates ProstT5, a bilingual protein sequence-and-structure
language model by Michael Heinzinger, Konstantin Weissenow, Joaquin Gomez Sanchez,
Adrian Hartmann, Martin Steinegger, and Burkhard Rost (Rostlab, TU Munich).

Source: https://github.com/mheinzinger/ProstT5
Model weights: https://huggingface.co/Rostlab/ProstT5
Paper: "ProstT5: Bilingual Language Model for Protein Sequence and Structure"
(bioRxiv, 2023; arXiv:2310.07083)

ProstT5 is released under the MIT License (see
https://github.com/mheinzinger/ProstT5/blob/main/LICENSE). The copyright holder
above is the upstream repository owner / lead author; confirm the exact line with
the authors if a precise attribution is required.
